Commands for configuring AI tooling integrations with fotingo.

Usage:
  fotingo ai [command]

Available Commands:
  setup       Install fotingo agent skills for supported AI providers

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for ai

Global Flags:
  -b, --branch string   Base branch override (default: auto-detect)
      --debug           Show diagnostic output (includes verbose)
      --json            Output results as JSON
      --no-color        Disable colored output
      --quiet           Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose         Show step-level progress output
  -y, --yes             Accept defaults without prompting

Use "fotingo ai [command] --help" for more information about a command.
